{"tid":522559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【上門報仇？】野豬闖南韓豬肉鍋店「掃場」 食客雞飛狗走逃命","createTime":"2018-01-07T16:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T17:15:46.000Z","uid":29627,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"818dfb3bb9c017f2eff00149be87e52a8f99e260","tid":522559,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:31:18.000Z","msg":"【上門報仇？】野豬闖南韓豬肉鍋店「掃場」 食客雞飛狗走逃命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180107/large/1515310481_bbb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180107%2Flarge%2F1515310481_bbb5.jpg&h=fbc33e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓慶尚北道龜尾（Gumi）一間豬肉泡菜鍋店，在元旦日突然有一隻野豬闖入，野豬還在店內亂竄，嚇得食客尖叫逃命。<br />\n<br />\n野豬先後撞開兩道門闖入店內，一開始沒有人發現牠，當牠跳上座位又發出聲響後，才有人驚覺不對勁。野豬先撞向牆壁，接著把目標轉向人群攻擊食客。<br />\n客人見狀嚇得起身逃命，有女生跳到椅子上、有人拿屏風掩護、也有人趁亂奪門而逃，整間餐廳亂成一團。大約4分鐘後，終於有一名男子拿起屏風當盾牌，才順利把野豬趕到店外。<br />\n泡菜鍋店新年伊始就有野豬來襲，南韓網友表示：「牠的名字是不是叫金正恩？」、「加肉不加價」、「如果是在中國，牠會直接被抓進廚房」，也有人誇獎牠：「真夠義氣，跑來拯救同胞了」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180108/57676639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57676639&d=C5URjvjJw%2FhmANx1N%2Fa7TzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=640cc3d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180108%2F57676639&h=e0b7abf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180108/57676639</a>"},{"pid":"27e81ef8cd216b6d9e210c3cab71b8350224dd11","tid":522559,"uid":121546,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:38:29.000Z","msg":"乜野豬唔係冇攻擊性既咩,定係新界果D野豬有靈性D?<br />\n新界果邊咁多野豬,好彩冇人受傷姐"},{"pid":"89d49f1c68e2d4e1109ee87c376b6bf3c0e1c288","tid":522559,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"27e81ef8cd216b6d9e210c3cab71b8350224dd11","tid":522559,"uid":121546,"like":1,"disli